---
title: Crispy Herb-Mustard Crusted Lamb Chops With Roasted Potatoes and Spring Peas
description: Enjoy "rack of lamb" vibes minus the fuss with this easy-to-make dinner! Lamb chops are crusted with Dijon mustard and herby panko. Served with savoury peas and roasted potatoes, it's a resto-worthy dish you can make yourself!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cotelettes-dagneau-en-croute-dherbes-et-de-moutarde-a99860e1.jpg
